#
# SLSI TOUCH driver configuration
#

config TOUCHSCREEN_SLSI_Y79A
        tristate "SLSI Touchscreen"
        depends on I2C
        help
          Say Y here if you want support for SLSI touchscreen controllers.
          If unsure, say N.

          To compile this driver as a module, choose M here: the
          module will be called sec_ts.

config TOUCHSCREEN_SEC_TS_GLOVEMODE
        tristate "Samsung Electronics Touchscreen"
        depends on I2C
        help
          Say Y here if you have a Samsung Electronics Touchscreen and want to enable
          support for the built-in touchscreen.

          If unsure, say N.
